% It is possible to request the presence of an incoming edge with the "*" symbol.
% In the example below, only occurrences of the verb "make" with an incoming edge roots are given

pattern { N [ upos=VERB, lemma="make"]; * -[root]-> N; }

% Warning: the clause "* -[root]-> N" is not equivalent to the clause "X -[root]-> N":
% The first is just an additional constraint, the second matches a new node "X"
